Air, makanan, segalanya.

00:15:23.851 --> 00:15:24.987
Beritahu aku.

00:15:32.324 --> 00:15:33.355
Dia tersedak.

00:15:33.766 --> 00:15:35.454
Gantung dia terbalik.

00:15:39.330 --> 00:15:40.361
Terbalik.

00:15:40.837 --> 00:15:42.064
Bagus.

00:15:44.873 --> 00:15:45.904
Gambar peta.

00:15:46.274 --> 00:15:48.670
Gambar arah!

00:15:53.784 --> 00:15:55.347
Tunjukkan pada kami!

00:16:09.994 --> 00:16:11.976
Kau mengalami hari berat, benar?

00:16:12.000 --> 00:16:13.200
Hari yang buruk.

00:16:14.773 --> 00:16:16.401
Kau pasti kelelahan.

00:16:18.235 --> 00:16:20.938
Cuma ada satu hal yang perlu
