Bawa dia, beri makan, mandikan.

00:16:38.490 --> 00:16:40.029
Gunakan air minum terbaik kita.

00:16:43.766 --> 00:16:45.230
Kalian berdua.

00:16:45.334 --> 00:16:46.728
Awasi dia, jaga dia tetap aman.

00:16:46.832 --> 00:16:48.631
Larang orang-orang
kasar ini mendekatinya.

